description:
Blessing of Sonic Fist Cief. Basic attack power increases by
200%. It is lifted when Cief is destroyed.
name: The Blessings of Secrecy

description:
Basic defense power increases by 300%. It will be lifted
when Affirbill is destroyed.
name: Guardian of Affirbill

description:
Basic defense power increases by 200%. There are cracks even
in its ironclad defense.
name: Echoes of Affirbill

description:
Available for use when grabbed by an enemy or downed. In
emergency, explode magical power to escape
name: Burst

description:
Charge attack. Inflict magical damage in a narrow area in
front with a powerful punch charged with magic.
name: Forte

description:
Obscene piercings attached to Ganelon's favorite woman. A
humiliating decoration unfitting for a noble lady.
name: Piercing of Subjection

description:
A distinctive tattoo that is applied to a favorite toy of an
Orc. Cannot be avoided to be regarded with contempt.
name: Orc Slave Mark

description:
Information about physical reactions caused by sexually
transmitted diseases and training. Objective descriptions to
specific acts.
name: Body

description:
Delicious homemade dishes with fresh ingredients grown in
the town. It's a cuisine that brings forth the power of
nature.
name: Buff: The lady's special dish

description:
A baked cookie, made by kneading wheat flour with milk. The
syrupy topping sprinkled on top evokes a rustic sweetness.
name: Buff: Simple baked sweets

description:
The abdomen swells only slightly, with little to no effect
on bodily movement yet.
name: Debuff: EarlyPregnancy

description:
The noticeable protrusion is clearly visible. Its weight
impedes Serena's movement.
name: Debuff: MidtermPregnancy

description:
Its abdomen is so swollen that it causes hindrance in daily
life. Combat is also out of the question.
name: Debuff: LatePregnancy

description:
Bathed her whole body in the Katherine's panacea. The
overwhelming pleasure was, however, still painful.
name: Love potion addiction

description:
Reinforcement of emotions such as fear towards specific
actions,  and expressing such emotions by feeling disgusted,
or crying out.
name: Heart

description:
I obey Guesclin's words. It is still in a mild state, and it
is possible to rebel if you feel uncomfortable.
name: Guesclin's Hypnosis Mild

description:
She submitted to Guesclin's words. The feelings of
discomfort faded, and come to accept Guesclin.
name: Guesclin's Hypnosis Moderate

description:
Guesclin's words will be accepted. Due to hypnosis, even
tastes and common sense are being violated.
name: Guesclin's Hypnosis Training

description:
Her mind has almost completely succumbed to Guesclin. If he
pushes her a bit, Serena's heart will fully surrender.
name: Guesclin's Hypnosis Severe

description:
Hearing their voice makes her heart freeze with fear. Even
if she tries to stand up, she won't be able to fight.
name: Trauma City Police Officer

description:
Her mind and body were overwhelmed by Ganelon. His will is
everything and anything else is worthless.
name: Trauma Ganelon

description:
She tasted extreme humiliation and feeling of liberation.
This continues to torment the proud and noble girl.
name: Trauma Excretion
